CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 1, 1947, pg. 15, reads: "Lyceum Leaders - High school students who are serving on the YMCA committee for a summer co-recreation camp, recently met to discuss plans for the venture, Jan. 20. Left to right are Joan Hawthorne, Danny Watkins, Jane Randall, Brady Nixon and Jeanne Adams. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: High school students Joan Hawthorne, Danny Watkins, Jane Randall holding pencil, Brady Nixon, and Jeanne Adams gathered for meeting about YMCA summer camp
